    <entry>
      <title>个人博客搭建记录（经验贴）</title>
      <link href="/2026/07/13/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/"/>
      <url>/2026/07/13/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="搭建篇"><a href="#搭建篇" class="headerlink" title="搭建篇"></a>搭建篇</h1><p>基于Hexo框架搭建github博客，主机是win11</p><p><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/github-pages">官方指南</a> and <a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aV411p7Bc?vd_source=1bab29b378adcb035a911f315d057785&spm_id_from=333.788.videopod.sections">参考视频</a></p><p>首先安装 <a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads">git</a> 和 <a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download">Node.js</a>，然后去学习一下git 和 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_59509843/article/details/139632151">github 之间的交互</a></p><hr><p>首先新建文件夹<code>Local repository</code>，右键点击<code> Git Bash Here</code> </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#设置仓库</span></span><br><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#配置账号和邮箱</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;Your name&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;Your email&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#配置ssh（方便远程登录）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#中间有需要选择的地方直接按回车就行。</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">&quot;Your email&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#查看C:\Users\Administrator下是否有.ssh文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#复制.ssh文件夹下id_rsa.pub文件中的内容（记事本打开）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#到github上 setting&gt;Account&gt;SSH and GPG&gt; NEW SSH key</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#最后邮箱会收到消息</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>拉取项目就点击github项目主页绿绿的<code>Code</code>，找到SSH即可</p><hr><p>新建文件夹 MyBlog，进入Bash，执行<code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code>安装Hexo工具</p><p>接下来初始化博客</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init myblogs</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> myblogs</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>hexo server</code> 启动服务，<code>http://localhost:4000/</code>本地游览器访问，出现界面就成功了</p><p>然后创建一个github仓库，名字必须是<code>github用户名.github.io</code>，勾选<code>Add a README file</code></p><p>创建后点击settings，在pages中就能看到自己的个人网站了！</p><p>回到<code>\MyBlog\myblogs</code> 找到_config.yml，用VS打开，定位到最后</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;git&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:Tenryon/Tenryon.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>repo格式通过上文提到的拉项目方法获取</p><p>关于branch的填写，必须要和博客 settings 中GitHub Pages部分指定的<strong>Branch</strong>保持一致。</p><p>在<code>\MyBlog\mybgs</code>，使用 <code>git bash</code>输入</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#手动确认一次主机密钥</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#等待回复后输入 yes</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>出现<code>INFO  Deploy done: git</code>后说明推送成功，这样就搭建好了</p><p><code>\MyBlog\myblogs\source\_posts</code> 下写md，然后执行下面代码更新(需要时间)</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#上传</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g -d</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#本地查看效果</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="美化篇"><a href="#美化篇" class="headerlink" title="美化篇"></a>美化篇</h1><p>采取主题为<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/21cfbf15/">ButterFly</a> 以及md前面的<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/dc584b87/">frontmatter</a></p><p>在博客根目录下myblog打开bash</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安裝穩定版本（推薦）</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><strong>使用主題</strong>: 修改您的 Hexo 配置檔案 <code>_config.yml</code>：</li></ol><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">butterfly</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li><strong>安裝依賴</strong>: 如果您尚未安裝 pug 和 stylus 渲染器，請執行：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样我们就安装好了butterfly主题</p><p>然后按自己的需求进行配置，参考<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/4aa8abbe/">配置</a>修改，由于细节太多和可复用性弱，请自行查阅喵~</p><blockquote><p>删除myblog 下面的<code>_config.landscape.yml</code>无影响<br>把<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/4aa8abbe/">butterfly的配置文件（放在开头）</a>复制到博客根目录，并重命名为 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code>，这样以后升级主题时就不会覆盖你的自定义设置</p></blockquote><h2 id="主题界面"><a href="#主题界面" class="headerlink" title="主题界面"></a>主题界面</h2><h3 id="标签页"><a href="#标签页" class="headerlink" title="标签页"></a>标签页</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建标签页</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到 <code>source/tags/index.md </code>這個文件</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: xxx的标签页</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-01-05 00:00:00</span><br><span class="line">type: &#x27;tags&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">orderby: random</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">order: 1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>参数</th><th>解释</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>type</td><td>【必須】頁面類型，必須為 tags</td></tr><tr><td>orderby</td><td>【可選】排序方式 ：<br/>random - 隨機排序 &#x2F; name - 標簽名字排序 &#x2F; length - 標簽數量排序</td></tr><tr><td>order</td><td>【可選】排序次序： 1（升序），-1（降序）</td></tr></tbody></table><p><code>hexo server </code> 本地查看<a href="http://localhost:4000/tags/">http://localhost:4000/tags/</a></p><h3 id="分类页"><a href="#分类页" class="headerlink" title="分类页"></a>分类页</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建分类页</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到 <code>source/categories/index.md </code>這個文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分類</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-01-05 00:00:00</span><br><span class="line">type: &#x27;categories&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>本地查看<a href="http://localhost:4000/categories/">http://localhost:4000/categories/</a></p><h3 id="友链"><a href="#友链" class="headerlink" title="友链"></a>友链</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建友链</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new page <span class="built_in">link</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到 <code>source/link/index.md </code>這個文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 友情鏈接</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-06-07 22:17:49</span><br><span class="line">type: &#x27;link&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加友链在 <code>source/_data/link.yml</code>中</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">link:</span> <span class="string">https://hexo.io/zh-tw/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar: https:</span> <span class="string">sdfsdf</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">descr:</span> <span class="string">快速、簡單且強大的網誌框架</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="404"><a href="#404" class="headerlink" title="404"></a>404</h3><p><code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 找到<code>error_404</code> 设置成<code>true</code>即可</p><h2 id="主题配置"><a href="#主题配置" class="headerlink" title="主题配置"></a>主题配置</h2><p>接下来的大部分操作在<code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> </p><h3 id="导航"><a href="#导航" class="headerlink" title="导航"></a>导航</h3><p>找到menu并解注释，要需求调整（||后面的是图标库）</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">主页:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">Archives:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">分类:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-folder-open</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">链接||fas</span> <span class="attr">fa-list:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">友情链接:</span> <span class="string">/link/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-link</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">关于:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-heart</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="代码块"><a href="#代码块" class="headerlink" title="代码块"></a>代码块</h3><blockquote><p>这个真要看文档调自己喜欢的风格了</p></blockquote><p>找到code_blocks</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#我只改了这个</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">height_limit:</span> <span class="number">250</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="社交图标"><a href="#社交图标" class="headerlink" title="社交图标"></a>社交图标</h3><p>Butterfly 支持 <a href="https://fontawesome.com/icons?from=io">font-awesome v6</a> 图标.</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">social:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">fab fa-github:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/xxxxx</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">Github</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">&quot;#hdhfbb&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">fas fa-envelope:</span> <span class="string">mailto:xxxxxx@gmail.com</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">Email</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">&quot;#000000&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h3><p>按<code>\MyBlog\myblogs\source\img </code>创建文件夹，以后将图片放到这里。路径是”.&#x2F;img&#x2F;xxx.jpg”</p><p>将一些头像，背景换了即可（这样你的博客就焕然一新了）</p><p>可以参考<a href="https://yangcheneee.github.io/posts/blog_butterfly/index.html#%E4%BA%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98">别人的替换</a></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#头像</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">img:</span> <span class="string">xxx</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#主页横幅</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">index_img:</span> <span class="string">xxx</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#默认其他横幅</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">default_top_img:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#背景</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">background:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="主页副标题"><a href="#主页副标题" class="headerlink" title="主页副标题"></a>主页副标题</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 首页的副标题设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 是否启用副标题</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 是否启用打字机效果</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">effect:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">loop:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 自定义 typed.js</span></span><br><spa